1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:01,867
[GRUNTS]

2
00:00:02,067 --> 00:00:03,267
[BOTH GROANS]

3
00:00:03,433 --> 00:00:05,733
<i> Roi, don't hurt my son!</i>

4
00:00:06,433 --> 00:00:08,467
<i>- Police!
- [GROANS]</i>

5
00:00:13,067 --> 00:00:14,967
[GROANING]

6
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:16,400
Where did you take Jade Almazan?

7
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:18,933
<i>I won't tell you if you
don't let me and Frida go!</i>

8
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:20,067
<i> Get off!</i>

9
00:00:20,233 --> 00:00:22,767
<i>- Run! After them!
- [GUNSHOTS]</i>

10
00:00:25,933 --> 00:00:26,967
[THUDS]

11
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:28,133
<i> Hey!</i>

12
00:00:31,900 --> 00:00:33,033
<i>- Gio!
- [GUNSHOTS]</i>

13
00:00:33,133 --> 00:00:35,467
<i>I'm not after your money
anymore, Gio.</i>

14
00:00:35,633 --> 00:00:36,933
<i> Just do it, Bok.</i>

15
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:38,600
<i>Don't drag my brothers
into this.</i>

16
00:00:38,767 --> 00:00:40,433
<i>I'll kill you  if something
happens to them.</i>

17
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,933
[GRUNTS]

18
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,267
<i>How does it feel
to be unlucky, Gio?</i>

19
00:00:45,133 --> 00:00:46,967
- [GRUNTING]
- [SCREAMS IN PAIN]

20
00:00:47,133 --> 00:00:52,100
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

21
00:00:52,267 --> 00:00:54,900
- [GIO GROANS IN PAIN]
- [LAUGHS]

22
00:00:58,133 --> 00:01:01,133
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

23
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,400
- [GIO GROANS]
- [LAUGHS]

24
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:06,567
- [GIO GRUNTS]
- [GROANS]

25
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:18,300
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

26
00:02:11,367 --> 00:02:13,133
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

27
00:02:13,233 --> 00:02:19,533
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

28
00:02:19,733 --> 00:02:22,533
[PANTING]

29
00:02:28,233 --> 00:02:29,533
[GROANS]

30
00:02:36,233 --> 00:02:37,833
[PHONE BEEPING]

31
00:02:37,933 --> 00:02:38,933
[GROANS]

32
00:02:39,067 --> 00:02:42,667
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

33
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:47,333
Just keep looking for Jade.

34
00:02:47,467 --> 00:02:49,267
- Yes, ma'am.
- [PHONE BUZZING]

35
00:02:49,433 --> 00:02:52,033
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

36
00:02:52,133 --> 00:02:53,267
Ma'am?

37
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,367
This is Edward Arellano.

38
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:59,900
Yes, ma'am. I just want
to ask for an update.

39
00:03:01,067 --> 00:03:03,800
Mr. Arellano,
we've arrested Roi.

40
00:03:05,833 --> 00:03:08,200
[EXHALES DEEPLY]
Okay.

41
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:09,867
How about Jade?

42
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,433
Where is she?

43
00:03:11,567 --> 00:03:13,467
<i>Has Roi told you
where she is?</i>

44
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,467
Not yet.

45
00:03:15,233 --> 00:03:16,633
Ma'am, we need
to find Jade.

46
00:03:17,967 --> 00:03:20,767
Mr. Arellano, we know our job.

47
00:03:20,933 --> 00:03:22,167
But for now,

48
00:03:22,300 --> 00:03:24,500
<i>you need to get out
of that place.</i>

49
00:03:24,667 --> 00:03:25,900
No.

50
00:03:26,033 --> 00:03:27,633
Ma'am, we can't leave yet.

51
00:03:27,767 --> 00:03:30,167
Roi must've hidden Jade
somewhere around here.

52
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:32,467
He's still using her
against her family.

53
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,500
That means Jade is here.

54
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:39,000
Mr. Arellano, our entire team
is still searching.

55
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:41,400
We'll update you.

56
00:03:43,633 --> 00:03:45,267
Okay, ma'am. Thank you.

57
00:03:48,267 --> 00:03:54,900
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

58
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,800
Jade. Jade.
Jade, where are you?

59
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:04,833
Jade!

60
00:04:06,067 --> 00:04:07,700
Jade, please show yourself.

61
00:04:07,833 --> 00:04:09,767
Jade. Jade!

62
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:12,267
Jade. Please show up.

63
00:04:13,367 --> 00:04:14,700
Where are you, Jade?

64
00:04:14,867 --> 00:04:16,533
Come on, Jade.

65
00:04:16,667 --> 00:04:21,200
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

66
00:04:21,367 --> 00:04:24,000
Jade. Jade, where are you?

67
00:04:25,067 --> 00:04:26,033
Jade!

68
00:04:28,767 --> 00:04:31,633
Jade, are you there?
Come on, Jade.

69
00:04:31,767 --> 00:04:33,667
Jade. Jade...

70
00:04:34,533 --> 00:04:36,067
Jade, please.

71
00:04:37,867 --> 00:04:38,567
Jade!

72
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:44,367
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

73
00:04:46,167 --> 00:04:47,700
[MUFFLED WAIL]

74
00:04:48,433 --> 00:04:49,533
[JADE SOBS]

75
00:04:55,267 --> 00:04:56,733
Jade.

76
00:04:56,867 --> 00:04:57,733
Jade!

77
00:04:58,667 --> 00:04:59,700
Jade...

78
00:04:59,833 --> 00:05:03,233
[PANTING]

79
00:05:03,433 --> 00:05:09,767
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

80
00:05:09,900 --> 00:05:14,833
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

81
00:05:18,067 --> 00:05:21,600
[MUFFLED SOBBING]

82
00:05:23,767 --> 00:05:25,933
[GRUNTING]

83
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:29,500
[BARRELS CLANK]

84
00:05:33,067 --> 00:05:33,933
[EDWARD] Jade.

85
00:05:39,333 --> 00:05:40,933
Jade. Jade.

86
00:05:41,067 --> 00:05:43,133
Jade, Jade, Jade.
Can you hear me, Jade?

87
00:05:43,267 --> 00:05:45,367
[JADE GROANING]

88
00:05:46,933 --> 00:05:48,700
[EDWARD] Jade. Jade.

89
00:05:48,833 --> 00:05:49,900
Jade, Jade.

90
00:05:50,933 --> 00:05:51,900
Jade.

91
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,067
[GRUNTING]

92
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,900
[METAL CLANKS]

93
00:06:02,667 --> 00:06:03,967
[METAL LID CLANKS]

94
00:06:04,133 --> 00:06:05,433
Jade.

95
00:06:05,567 --> 00:06:08,633
Jade, Jade, Jade,
Jade, Jade, Jade...

96
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,067
Come here.

97
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,567
[EDWARD GRUNTING]

98
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,467
Jade...

99
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,833
Jade, Jade.

100
00:06:16,967 --> 00:06:17,967
Jade, wake up.

101
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:19,667
Jade, Jade, Jade.

102
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,500
[EDWARD] Jade. Wake up, Jade.

103
00:06:22,633 --> 00:06:24,500
Jade, Jade, Jade!

104
00:06:24,633 --> 00:06:26,133
Wake up! Jade!

105
00:06:26,267 --> 00:06:28,100
Jade? Jade. Wake up, Jade.

106
00:06:29,133 --> 00:06:30,633
[EDWARD] Jade, wake up...

107
00:06:32,767 --> 00:06:33,633
Jade.

108
00:06:33,767 --> 00:06:34,667
Wake up.

109
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,000
[WHIMPERS]

110
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,967
[SOBS]

111
00:06:45,067 --> 00:06:47,133
You're safe. You're okay.

112
00:06:47,233 --> 00:06:48,800
I'm here now.

113
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:50,533
I'm here, Jade.

114
00:06:50,667 --> 00:06:52,200
- I'm here, okay?
- [CRIES]

115
00:06:52,333 --> 00:06:55,133
Jade... It's okay. I'm here.

116
00:06:55,233 --> 00:06:58,200
No... No. No.

117
00:06:58,333 --> 00:07:00,933
Huh? Huh, Jade? Jade.

118
00:07:01,967 --> 00:07:03,600
[SOBBING]

119
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,767
[EDWARD] I'm here, Jade.

120
00:07:06,533 --> 00:07:07,867
I'm here.

121
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,267
Jade...

122
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,333
You're all right.

123
00:07:10,467 --> 00:07:12,033
You're all right.

124
00:07:15,333 --> 00:07:17,067
- Jade.
- [JADE SOBS]

125
00:07:19,233 --> 00:07:20,633
[SOBBING]

126
00:07:20,767 --> 00:07:26,800
[EMOTIONAL MUSIC PLAYING]

127
00:07:33,433 --> 00:07:36,533
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

128
00:07:39,567 --> 00:07:42,967
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

129
00:07:44,167 --> 00:07:45,800
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

130
00:07:53,267 --> 00:07:55,100
- [THUDS]
- [LEAVES RUSTLING]

131
00:07:55,233 --> 00:07:56,567
[KIKO GRUNTS]

132
00:07:58,933 --> 00:08:00,100
[KIKO] Gio!

133
00:08:00,233 --> 00:08:01,600
[KIKO GRUNTING]

134
00:08:04,033 --> 00:08:05,400
Gio!

135
00:08:05,533 --> 00:08:06,433
Kiko!

136
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,033
[PANTS]

137
00:08:08,133 --> 00:08:09,233
[GIO] Martin...

138
00:08:09,367 --> 00:08:11,100
Gio, hold on tight!

139
00:08:11,233 --> 00:08:12,767
- Hold on, please!
- Please!

140
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:19,500
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

141
00:08:20,133 --> 00:08:21,767
[GRUNTING]

142
00:08:28,467 --> 00:08:30,067
[GRUNTING]

143
00:08:35,067 --> 00:08:35,633
[GIO GRUNTS]

144
00:08:35,633 --> 00:08:37,300
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

145
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:38,300
Bok...

146
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:41,100
We'll get away from them, okay?

147
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:42,267
- Just hang in there!
- Gio!

148
00:08:42,267 --> 00:08:44,633
Gio! Gio, stay awake!

149
00:08:44,633 --> 00:08:45,733
Stay awake, please!

150
00:08:45,733 --> 00:08:46,933
We'll go to the hospital!

151
00:08:46,933 --> 00:08:47,933
Promise!

152
00:08:47,933 --> 00:08:48,967
Stay awake!

153
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:50,800
[KIKO] Gio!

154
00:08:51,733 --> 00:08:53,633
[KIKO, MARTIN GRUNTING]

155
00:08:53,633 --> 00:08:54,433
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

156
00:08:54,467 --> 00:08:55,467
[KIKO GROANING]

157
00:08:55,467 --> 00:08:57,167
Kiko, don't let go!

158
00:09:01,033 --> 00:09:03,900
[GIO GRUNTING WITH STRAIN]

159
00:09:09,467 --> 00:09:12,667
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

160
00:09:12,667 --> 00:09:13,967
[MUSIC FADING]

161
00:09:13,967 --> 00:09:15,433
[ROI] I didn't do anything!

162
00:09:15,433 --> 00:09:17,933
Why are you locking me up?
I'm innocent!

163
00:09:17,933 --> 00:09:19,167
- [GATE BANGING]
- [LOCK CLANKING]

164
00:09:19,167 --> 00:09:20,633
I didn't kill them!

165
00:09:21,167 --> 00:09:23,933
I didn't kill them!
I've never killed anybody!

166
00:09:23,933 --> 00:09:25,467
Believe me!

167
00:09:25,467 --> 00:09:27,033
- That's enough!
- [HEAVY BREATHS]

168
00:09:27,033 --> 00:09:28,433
[ROI]
It wasn't me who killed them.

169
00:09:28,467 --> 00:09:30,233
- [GLOOMY MUSIC PLAYING]
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]

170
00:09:30,233 --> 00:09:32,133
Mrs. Almazan has
identified you.

171
00:09:32,133 --> 00:09:34,700
She claimed you were there
at the time when both men died.

172
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:36,200
[ROI BREATHES DEEPLY]

173
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:39,833
I went there for Frida.

174
00:09:39,833 --> 00:09:41,067
[BREATH QUIVERING]

175
00:09:41,067 --> 00:09:44,167
I went there for Frida.
For her safety!

176
00:09:44,167 --> 00:09:47,333
And because you've long had
feelings for Mrs. Almazan,

177
00:09:47,333 --> 00:09:49,700
you used the opportunity

178
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:52,000
to get Frederico
out of the picture.

179
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:55,300
Then you killed his friend too
so there would be no witness.

180
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:58,167
All of this, just to carry out
your plan with Mrs. Almazan.

181
00:09:58,167 --> 00:09:59,167
[ROI CRYING]

182
00:09:59,167 --> 00:10:01,967
I didn't do anything.

183
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,367
[GLOOMY MUSIC CONTINUES]

184
00:10:03,367 --> 00:10:05,467
They were dead
by the time I saw them!

185
00:10:06,067 --> 00:10:07,400
[JUSTIN] You're a liar.

186
00:10:08,033 --> 00:10:09,400
You killed my dad!

187
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,000
We welcomed you!

188
00:10:11,767 --> 00:10:13,767
My parents trusted you!

189
00:10:13,767 --> 00:10:14,767
[ROI SNIFFLES]

190
00:10:14,767 --> 00:10:15,900
[HANDCUFFS RATTLING]

191
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:17,333
Justin...

192
00:10:17,733 --> 00:10:19,933
- Justin, I didn't kill anyone.
- [MOCKING TONE] Huh? Huh?

193
00:10:19,933 --> 00:10:21,033
[JUSTIN] Crazy!

194
00:10:21,033 --> 00:10:22,233
You're crazy!

195
00:10:22,233 --> 00:10:23,100
[GLOOMY MUSIC CONTINUES]

196
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:25,367
- [LEON] Justin, let's go.
- Huh?!

197
00:10:25,367 --> 00:10:28,033
You're going to rot in prison!
You murderer!

198
00:10:28,033 --> 00:10:29,033
[SCOFFS]

199
00:10:29,033 --> 00:10:29,900
Let's go!

200
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:32,767
[ROI]
The only crime I committed...

201
00:10:32,767 --> 00:10:34,467
was loving Frida.

202
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:38,233
I swear to all of you,

203
00:10:38,233 --> 00:10:41,533
my conscience is clean!

204
00:10:41,533 --> 00:10:42,767
[PANTING]

205
00:10:42,767 --> 00:10:44,433
I didn't kill Michael.

206
00:10:45,233 --> 00:10:47,033
I didn't kill Frederico.

207
00:10:47,033 --> 00:10:54,000
[GLOOMY MUSIC CONTINUES]

208
00:11:02,533 --> 00:11:04,333
[ROI CRYING]

209
00:11:06,067 --> 00:11:07,067
[PRESSURE CUFF UNFASTENS]

210
00:11:07,067 --> 00:11:09,733
[SIREN WAILING
IN THE DISTANCE]

211
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:12,100
[FRIDA] Jade.

212
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:14,000
- Jade, my daughter.
- Mom?

213
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,300
- [SOFTLY] Jade.
- [VOICE BREAKING] Mom.

214
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,233
[SOBBING] Mom, Mom...

215
00:11:17,833 --> 00:11:19,467
Mom... Mom...

216
00:11:19,467 --> 00:11:20,833
[MELLOW MUSIC PLAYING]

217
00:11:20,833 --> 00:11:23,100
[FRIDA] Thank God you're safe.

218
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:24,333
Thank you.

219
00:11:24,333 --> 00:11:26,233
[FRIDA]
I'm so sorry, sweetheart.

220
00:11:27,167 --> 00:11:30,400
My dear, I'm so sorry
I was late.

221
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,867
Your life should never
have been in danger.

222
00:11:34,333 --> 00:11:36,300
[JADE SOBBING]

223
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:38,933
Mom, it's not your fault, okay?

224
00:11:38,933 --> 00:11:41,067
- [MELLOW MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [BOTH SNIFFLING]

225
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:42,300
Roi...

226
00:11:42,867 --> 00:11:44,467
Mom, it was Roi's.

227
00:11:44,467 --> 00:11:46,133
[BREATH QUIVERING,
EXHALES HEAVILY]

228
00:11:46,133 --> 00:11:47,933
He's gone, sweetheart.

229
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,600
He's been caught.

230
00:11:51,333 --> 00:11:53,300
No one will hurt you anymore.

231
00:11:54,467 --> 00:11:57,033
- [FRIDA SNIFFLING, WHIMPERS]
- [JADE SOBBING]

232
00:11:57,033 --> 00:11:58,267
[FRIDA] My baby...

233
00:11:58,267 --> 00:11:59,633
[MELLOW MUSIC CONTINUES]

234
00:11:59,633 --> 00:12:01,500
- I'm sorry.
- I love you, Mom.

235
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,567
I love you.

236
00:12:03,267 --> 00:12:04,433
[KISSES, CRIES]

237
00:12:06,533 --> 00:12:07,567
Mom.

238
00:12:08,467 --> 00:12:09,467
Let's go?

239
00:12:11,833 --> 00:12:13,433
Let's go, Mom.

240
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:16,833
Let's go.

241
00:12:17,567 --> 00:12:20,333
Slow and steady, alright?

242
00:12:20,333 --> 00:12:27,300
[MELLOW MUSIC CONTINUES]

243
00:12:29,167 --> 00:12:30,900
[MARINA SIGHING]

244
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:35,067
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

245
00:12:35,067 --> 00:12:36,400
I'll get going.

246
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,633
The rest of us already
went ahead.

247
00:12:39,333 --> 00:12:42,433
It's Michael Fernandez's
children who need help now.

248
00:12:43,167 --> 00:12:44,833
What happened to them?

249
00:12:45,633 --> 00:12:48,467
Bok ambushed them.

250
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:51,600
But don't worry,
I'll take care of it.

251
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,033
You should go ahead.

252
00:12:53,033 --> 00:12:54,267
[MOROSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

253
00:12:54,267 --> 00:12:55,333
Okay.

254
00:12:57,267 --> 00:12:59,000
[FOOTSTEPS RECEDING]

255
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:11,667
[SIREN WAILING]

256
00:13:11,667 --> 00:13:14,933
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

257
00:13:14,933 --> 00:13:15,967
[DOORS OPEN]

258
00:13:16,533 --> 00:13:18,033
[HURRIED FOOTSTEPS]

259
00:13:18,033 --> 00:13:19,167
[REAR CAR DOOR OPENS]

260
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:23,533
[MARTIN] Doc, please hurry!

261
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,733
- Doc...
- Doc! Nurse, please!

262
00:13:27,733 --> 00:13:29,233
Nurse, my brother! Save him!

263
00:13:29,233 --> 00:13:30,233
- Please!
- [NURSE] Get checked, too!

264
00:13:30,233 --> 00:13:32,567
[KIKO] No! Nurse, just focus
on our brother!

265
00:13:32,567 --> 00:13:34,067
He's dying!

266
00:13:34,067 --> 00:13:35,067
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

267
00:13:35,067 --> 00:13:36,567
What about Bok?
He might come back for us.

268
00:13:36,567 --> 00:13:39,500
He won't. The cops are already
after him and his crew, okay?

269
00:13:41,733 --> 00:13:42,867
This way, hurry!

270
00:13:42,867 --> 00:13:45,233
Nurse, where's
the emergency room?

271
00:13:45,233 --> 00:13:46,233
[NURSE] This way.

272
00:13:46,233 --> 00:13:47,833
This way? Thank you.

273
00:13:48,067 --> 00:13:50,767
[CHESKA] Kiko! Kiko!

274
00:13:50,767 --> 00:13:52,167
- [TRIXIE] Oh my god, Martin!
- [CHESKA] Kiko!

275
00:13:53,467 --> 00:13:55,233
- Ouch!
- What happened?

276
00:13:55,267 --> 00:13:57,067
[OVERLAPPING CHATTER]

277
00:13:57,067 --> 00:13:58,500
[CHESKA] What happened to you?

278
00:13:58,500 --> 00:14:01,300
[OVERLAPPING CHATTER]

279
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,733
[CHESKA CRYING]
You're so reckless!

280
00:14:02,733 --> 00:14:04,567
- What happened to you?
- That's enough, that's enough.

281
00:14:04,567 --> 00:14:05,967
- I'm okay now.
- He has so many bruises

282
00:14:05,967 --> 00:14:07,067
on his lips and nose.

283
00:14:07,067 --> 00:14:10,000
- Why did you do that, Kiko?
- On the nose too?

284
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,133
Are you really okay?
Let's run some tests, please.

285
00:14:12,133 --> 00:14:14,500
- You may be injured.
- [SIGHS] Trixie.

286
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:16,000
- [SNIFFLING]
- [MARTIN] I'm okay.

287
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,600
- [TRIXIE BREATHES OUT]
- Promise.

288
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:23,100
[SARI CRYING]

289
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,533
[CHESKA] Sari?

290
00:14:25,967 --> 00:14:27,800
[VOICE SHAKING] Uh, don't worry
about me, sir.

291
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:29,833
I'm okay.

292
00:14:29,833 --> 00:14:32,000
These are, uh. Happy tears!

293
00:14:32,667 --> 00:14:34,800
I'm happy that you're okay.
Um--

294
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,967
Wait a sec. Where's Gio?

295
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:41,600
He's severely hurt.

296
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:47,167
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

297
00:14:47,167 --> 00:14:49,733
My god, Martin,
what even happened?

298
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,933
[BLOOD PRESSURE CUFF CRUNCHES]

299
00:14:57,933 --> 00:14:59,833
I know you want
to go home already.

300
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:04,133
But we need to make sure
that you're okay.

301
00:15:04,167 --> 00:15:05,933
[WHEELS RATTLING]

302
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:08,000
[SNIFFLES]

303
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:11,800
I'm sorry I couldn't help you.

304
00:15:13,867 --> 00:15:16,000
I'm sorry I wasn't there
when you were alone.

305
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:21,667
[MELANCHOLIC MUSIC PLAYING]

306
00:15:21,667 --> 00:15:23,667
You don't have
to say that, Luna.

307
00:15:25,233 --> 00:15:27,167
But I made a promise to Dad.

308
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:30,833
I told him I'd do anything
for our family.

309
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:34,167
And that includes
being a good sister to you.

310
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,167
[SNIFFLES]

311
00:15:40,733 --> 00:15:42,867
I know you're trying
your best, Luna.

312
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,033
[JADE SNIFFLES]

313
00:15:46,033 --> 00:15:49,200
You don't have to blame
yourself for everything

314
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,900
that's happening to us.

315
00:15:51,867 --> 00:15:52,933
Okay?

316
00:15:52,933 --> 00:15:59,767
[MELANCHOLIC MUSIC CONTINUES]

317
00:15:59,767 --> 00:16:01,667
[SNIFFLES, SIGHS]

318
00:16:02,333 --> 00:16:04,067
[LUNA SNIFFLING]

319
00:16:04,067 --> 00:16:05,633
[LUNA] Oh, they're here.

320
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,267
[JADE] Leon!

321
00:16:09,267 --> 00:16:10,867
- How are you?
- Leon.

322
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:12,867
[LEON EXHALES HEAVILY]

323
00:16:12,867 --> 00:16:16,067
Leon, the doctor said
I can go home already.

324
00:16:17,767 --> 00:16:20,000
Leon, any update?
What did the police say?

325
00:16:20,767 --> 00:16:22,900
Roi is already jailed
for kidnapping Jade.

326
00:16:23,133 --> 00:16:25,367
But for the murder of Dad
and Uncle Mike, uh...

327
00:16:26,733 --> 00:16:28,667
Our lawyers will have
to look into it first.

328
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,900
What's up?

329
00:16:31,900 --> 00:16:33,067
Hm?

330
00:16:33,067 --> 00:16:34,333
[CHUCKLES]

331
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,233
I told you to be careful.

332
00:16:36,933 --> 00:16:38,367
If it hurts somewhere,
tell us, okay?

333
00:16:39,900 --> 00:16:40,933
[SNIFFLES]

334
00:16:42,767 --> 00:16:44,133
What about Mom?

335
00:16:44,133 --> 00:16:45,400
Where's Mom?

336
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,933
They're still checking up
with her.

337
00:16:49,833 --> 00:16:50,967
- I need to talk to Mom.
- Jade, Jade.

338
00:16:50,967 --> 00:16:53,433
- Just rest for now.
- I have to talk to Mom, please.

339
00:16:53,433 --> 00:16:55,800
- You have to rest.
- Please, just for a moment.

340
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:57,000
[FRIDA] Jade.

341
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,933
[JADE CRYING]

342
00:16:58,933 --> 00:17:00,067
Jade.

343
00:17:00,067 --> 00:17:07,033
[MELANCHOLIC MUSIC CONTINUES]

344
00:17:09,133 --> 00:17:10,133
[JADE SOBS]

345
00:17:10,133 --> 00:17:11,300
Are you okay?

346
00:17:12,333 --> 00:17:14,700
I'm so sorry, Mom.

347
00:17:15,433 --> 00:17:17,400
I'm so sorry.

348
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:22,133
[CRYING] Jade, you don't
have to apologize.

349
00:17:22,467 --> 00:17:25,333
It's Roi's fault, not yours.

350
00:17:26,333 --> 00:17:27,667
No, Mom...

351
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,833
No apology would ever be enough

352
00:17:29,833 --> 00:17:32,133
for all of the things I've done

353
00:17:32,133 --> 00:17:33,800
and said to you.

354
00:17:35,167 --> 00:17:36,333
I'm so sorry.

355
00:17:36,933 --> 00:17:39,000
I'm sorry... I'm sorry...

356
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,833
[SMOOCHES] It's okay, Jade.

357
00:17:40,833 --> 00:17:41,967
It's not.

358
00:17:42,700 --> 00:17:44,233
Jade, listen to me.

359
00:17:46,833 --> 00:17:47,900
My dear,

360
00:17:48,733 --> 00:17:50,200
I'm your mother.

361
00:17:50,967 --> 00:17:54,200
There's nothing you can do
that I won't be able to forgive.

362
00:17:54,200 --> 00:18:01,167
[MELANCHOLIC MUSIC CONTINUES]

363
00:18:04,067 --> 00:18:05,767
[JADE SOBBING]

364
00:18:06,367 --> 00:18:08,233
[SNIFFLES, SIGHS]

365
00:18:08,233 --> 00:18:10,967
[FRIDA SOBBING]

366
00:18:16,067 --> 00:18:21,000
[EMOTIONAL MUSIC PLAYING]

367
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,967
Your Dad will never be able
to forgive me

368
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,867
if even one of you disappears.

369
00:18:25,067 --> 00:18:27,867
And I will never be able
to forgive myself either.

370
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:32,900
Thank God we are all safe.

371
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:39,867
[EMOTIONAL MUSIC CONTINUES]

372
00:18:41,267 --> 00:18:44,000
[PHONE RINGING]

373
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,233
- Luna.
- Kiko.

374
00:18:46,033 --> 00:18:48,300
I was just trying to call you
to ask about Jade.

375
00:18:48,767 --> 00:18:49,900
Ho-- How is she?

376
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:50,900
Wh-- Why are you here?

377
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:53,400
She's alright.
Ho-- How about your family?

378
00:18:55,567 --> 00:18:57,967
That Roi is sick in the head.

379
00:18:57,967 --> 00:18:59,500
He'll rot in jail.

380
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:03,900
What about Jade, is she okay?
How about Aunt Frida?

381
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:06,067
Jade is doing fine.

382
00:19:06,433 --> 00:19:08,833
Mom was just checked recently
and she's fine too.

383
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:11,100
What about you? Your family?

384
00:19:11,100 --> 00:19:12,567
What on earth happened?

385
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:14,300
[SIGHS]

386
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:16,133
Well... [INHALES SHARPLY]

387
00:19:16,133 --> 00:19:18,167
Gio is the one
who got hurt really badly.

388
00:19:18,533 --> 00:19:20,333
Why? What happened to Gio?

389
00:19:21,567 --> 00:19:23,867
We were on the way
to your place.

390
00:19:24,233 --> 00:19:25,433
But we were waylaid
by Bok and the others.

391
00:19:25,433 --> 00:19:28,100
You remember that guest
who caused a mess at the hotel?

392
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,267
It was him?

393
00:19:30,167 --> 00:19:31,967
He wanted
to exact revenge on Gio

394
00:19:31,967 --> 00:19:34,567
so they chased one another,
hit each other,

395
00:19:34,567 --> 00:19:36,133
and now he's all beat up.

396
00:19:36,467 --> 00:19:38,067
How did he get beat up?

397
00:19:40,467 --> 00:19:42,100
He got stabbed.

398
00:19:45,233 --> 00:19:46,900
Where is Bok and the others now?

399
00:19:48,167 --> 00:19:49,933
The police is currently
looking for them.

400
00:19:50,233 --> 00:19:53,900
I hope he gets caught already
so him and Roi can rot together.

401
00:19:56,967 --> 00:19:58,400
Are you okay, Luna?

402
00:19:58,400 --> 00:20:02,967
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

403
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,333
Well then, you should head back
to your siblings, Kiko.

404
00:20:05,967 --> 00:20:07,300
Get some rest yourself.

405
00:20:07,933 --> 00:20:09,300
Let's keep in touch.

406
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:11,933
Alright.

407
00:20:11,933 --> 00:20:13,633
[BREATHES DEEPLY] Thanks.

408
00:20:13,633 --> 00:20:20,600
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

409
00:20:24,933 --> 00:20:26,400
- [SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]
- [KNOB CLICKS]

410
00:20:34,267 --> 00:20:35,167
[DOOR CLOSES]

411
00:20:35,333 --> 00:20:39,467
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

412
00:20:54,400 --> 00:21:01,433
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

413
00:21:06,033 --> 00:21:07,667
<i> I hope you get well soon.</i>

414
00:21:07,833 --> 00:21:14,700
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

415
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:23,333
[FOOTSTEPS RETREATING]

416
00:21:23,433 --> 00:21:24,533
[DOOR OPENS]

417
00:21:29,567 --> 00:21:31,667
[KNOB CLICKS, DOOR CLOSES]

418
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:33,733
Get him!

419
00:21:33,867 --> 00:21:34,733
Where's Bok?

420
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:36,167
I don't know!

421
00:21:36,267 --> 00:21:37,833
- Bring him in.
- Come on.

422
00:21:37,933 --> 00:21:44,900
- [FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]
- [WAVES CRASHING]

423
00:21:50,133 --> 00:21:51,267
[FOREBODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

424
00:21:51,433 --> 00:21:52,767
[TWIG CRACKS]

425
00:21:52,933 --> 00:21:54,767
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

426
00:21:54,933 --> 00:21:55,867
[GUN CLICKS]

427
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:57,833
[MAN] Hey!

428
00:21:57,967 --> 00:21:59,933
I got this. Bring him in.

429
00:22:00,067 --> 00:22:01,500
- Let's go.
- Hurry up!

430
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:09,033
[WATER SPLASHING]

431
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:25,867
- [TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [LEAVES RUSTLING]

432
00:22:40,833 --> 00:22:47,800
- [TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [WAVES CRASHING]

433
00:23:00,133 --> 00:23:03,000
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

434
00:23:03,133 --> 00:23:05,133
[BOK SCREAMING IN DISTANCE] Aah!

435
00:23:07,367 --> 00:23:09,800
[FOOTSTEPS RUNNING IN SAND]

436
00:23:09,933 --> 00:23:12,767
[WATER SPLASHES]

437
00:23:27,833 --> 00:23:34,800
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

438
00:23:36,633 --> 00:23:38,667
[LIQUID TRICKLING]

439
00:23:50,333 --> 00:23:51,333
Bok?

440
00:23:51,467 --> 00:23:58,867
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

441
00:24:02,233 --> 00:24:04,300
<i> Welcome to Hotel 88!</i>

442
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,567
<i> The most awaited...</i>

443
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:07,667
<i> Gio's return!</i>

444
00:24:07,833 --> 00:24:08,867
<i> Back to normal then?</i>

445
00:24:09,033 --> 00:24:10,167
<i> No.</i>

446
00:24:10,333 --> 00:24:12,467
<i> My siblings are in danger.</i>

447
00:24:12,567 --> 00:24:14,200
<i> I need to protect them.</i>

448
00:24:15,233 --> 00:24:17,167
<i>Why do you have
Dad's laptop, Leon?</i>

449
00:24:17,267 --> 00:24:19,000
<i>I don't have reasons
to stay here anymore.</i>

450
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:20,367
<i>You should not
have been dragged.</i>

451
00:24:20,533 --> 00:24:22,700
<i>If you think justice
has been served</i>

452
00:24:22,867 --> 00:24:24,333
<i> for your father's death,</i>

453
00:24:24,433 --> 00:24:25,467
<i> you're wrong.</i>

454
00:24:25,567 --> 00:24:29,133
<i>The real killer
is still out and free.</i>

